{"id": 2649, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x全新一代凯迪拉克CT6】汽车领域有哪些事之前只敢想，现在却不断突破你想象？", "description": "外观内饰算是小操作，让我们来谈谈科技的飞跃", "record_count": 12838, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2018112722412718gtbMvehBSp2lKc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 313858, "content": "汽车可以上天入地", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433817}, {"id": 313859, "content": "自动驾驶系统", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434004}, {"id": 313861, "content": "自动驾驶，无需人的操作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433857}, {"id": 313862, "content": "纯电动车？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433827}, {"id": 313863, "content": "不了解", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433944}, {"id": 313864, "content": "移动音响", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433898}, {"id": 313609, "content": "小时候有个梦想 造一辆自己给自己充电的车，车轱辘发电 地面也发电 好像越来越近啦！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1391, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 313865, "content": "变形金刚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433871}, {"id": 313866, "content": "汽车房子，俗称房车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434022}, {"id": 313867, "content": "遥控汽车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434039}, {"id": 337933, "content": "🚗会飞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 313617, "content": "新的前脸 眼睛（大灯）的设计，真的有S级的气质！一秒钟草", "image": null, "praise_count": 976, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733477}, {"id": 313620, "content": "贾跃亭都能造车了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 911, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 313621, "content": "车内自带按摩椅！还有音效超棒的音响放自己喜欢的歌 可比去spa方便多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1326, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941471}, {"id": 313622, "content": "ABCD柱仍挡视线；裸车仍无法左右平移；我简直不敢想象，这行业惰性有多大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108298}, {"id": 313625, "content": "车辆系统跟软件能自己更新最好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139257}, {"id": 313626, "content": "我能跟车对话了，车还能给我讲笑话哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 464, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969118}, {"id": 313627, "content": "不瞒你说，我这种细节控，其实还是会看内饰皮革缝线的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 313629, "content": "混合动力车的飞速发展", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269958}, {"id": 313631, "content": "CT6真的逼格超高 你值得拥有", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433820}, {"id": 313632, "content": "全触屏跟语音控制 十几年前的想法 近年来终于实现了超激动", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433791}, {"id": 313633, "content": "小时候想过陆海两栖汽车 不过现在好像还没有吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433865}, {"id": 313634, "content": "以前想过可以将导航之类的影像投射在挡风玻璃上 竟然实现了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434045}, {"id": 313635, "content": "小时候想汽车能跟人一样可以智能对话 现在抖音上全是这个哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433931}, {"id": 313636, "content": "说一个很早就实现了的 汽车座椅能加热 哈哈哈这简直就是冬天不热星人的福音", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433845}, {"id": 313637, "content": "语音控制！！！我的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433971}, {"id": 313638, "content": "新能源 小时候学到石油战争的时候 总想着有一天不用汽油多好啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434051}, {"id": 313639, "content": "无人驾驶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434006}, {"id": 313640, "content": "以前一家人一起去外地玩的时候 多希望车后座能放倒 然后当场躺在上面 终于实现了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433809}, {"id": 313641, "content": "可以自己倒🚗*入*酷", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433984}, {"id": 313642, "content": "自动关门", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434041}, {"id": 313643, "content": "自动刹车系统", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433767}, {"id": 313644, "content": "绝对是自动驾驶！！以前看电影的时候觉得好厉害 现在竟然实现了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433946}, {"id": 313645, "content": "远程遥控 启动开空调 夏天怕热星人的福音", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433766}, {"id": 313646, "content": "手机远程控制 我现在看车展 分分钟觉得他们会变成汽车人 太智能了都", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433825}, {"id": 313648, "content": "我是来夸CT6的！！在他面前 宝马奥迪都是鸡肋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433846}, {"id": 313649, "content": "外观内饰的进步也是进步！灯头真的是越来越好看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433863}, {"id": 313651, "content": "车辆系统的更新 以前还要约时间去4s店 现在远程更新 方便多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433826}, {"id": 313652, "content": "你好，主人。感觉自己养了一只小宠物，智能语音系统真的太棒了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434003}, {"id": 313654, "content": "全景天窗！！我的大爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433906}, {"id": 313655, "content": "车外控制驾驶 雨天不用撑伞去车边 车可以来接我啦哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433770}, {"id": 313656, "content": "上车睡觉，下车拍照\n上车自动驾驶，下车扫码自动停车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511176}, {"id": 313661, "content": "以前营销靠砸钱。现在靠水军。", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140184}, {"id": 313662, "content": "无人驾驶", "image": 